Hey, big fella!

7
00:01:43,920 --> 00:01:46,184
Help me make the beds
in the living room.

8
00:01:46,389 --> 00:01:47,549
Come on down here!

9
00:01:47,757 --> 00:01:49,691
Hey, son!

10
00:01:50,627 --> 00:01:53,960
Big fella.
