42
00:03:13,776 --> 00:03:15,243
Here's a voltage adapter!

43
00:03:15,445 --> 00:03:19,074
God, you're getting heavy!
Go pack your suitcase.

44
00:03:20,416 --> 00:03:23,317
Pack my suitcase?

45
00:03:23,786 --> 00:03:26,050
- Where's the shampoo?
- I don't live here.

46
00:03:26,256 --> 00:03:28,486
